<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:15:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>法国酒精出口在2024年连续第二年减弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-alcohol-exports-weaken-second-straight-year-2024-2025-02-11/</link><description>行业集团周二表示，法国葡萄酒和烈酒出口连续第二年下降了，因为该行业与价格较低，中国市场和关税威胁较低，对高级葡萄酒的需求较弱。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-alcohol-exports-weaken-second-straight-year-2024-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普金属关税推动黄金，压力中国钢铁股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trump-metals-tariffs-propel-gold-pressure-china-steel-shares-2025-02-11/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对钢铁和铝的25％关税使黄金记录了贸易冲突和通货膨胀的担忧，而一些国家对谈判的希望和中国钢铁公司的份额承受了压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:37:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/trump-metals-tariffs-propel-gold-pressure-china-steel-shares-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>一月份的近一年中，中国的汽车销售职位最大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-car-sales-january-fall-12-year-earlier-2025-02-11/</link><description>一月份，中国的汽车销售额下降了12％，这是自9月以来的首次下降，是一年来最大的下降，因为汽车制造商在世界上最大的汽车市场上为激烈的竞争做好了努力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 08:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-car-sales-january-fall-12-year-earlier-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>美国向印度的煤炭出口预计将由于中国关税而上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-coal-exports-india-expected-rise-due-china-tariffs-2025-02-11/</link><description>五名行业官员说，在中国对美国的能源进口征收关税之后，预计美国将增加对印度的煤炭出口，这可能会侵蚀澳大利亚和俄罗斯在印度市场的市场份额。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/us-coal-exports-india-expected-rise-due-china-tariffs-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>百度首席执行官说，尽管DeepSeek的成功，仍然需要更多的人工智能支出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-ceo-says-more-ai-spend-still-needed-despite-deepseeks-success-2025-02-11/</link><description>百度首席执行官罗宾·李（Robin Li）周二表示，尽管DeepSeek挑战了大型AI模型的成本效率，但仍需要对数据中心和云基础设施的投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:39:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-ceo-says-more-ai-spend-still-needed-despite-deepseeks-success-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>韩国法院清除了汇丰银行违反了短销售规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/south-korean-court-clears-hsbc-charges-violating-short-selling-rules-yonhap-2025-02-11/</link><description>一名法院官员说，韩国法院周二因违反该国的卖空规则而被判无罪释放汇丰银行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:21:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/south-korean-court-clears-hsbc-charges-violating-short-selling-rules-yonhap-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯能源官员说，美国制裁不应阻碍印度的石油贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-energy-official-says-us-sanctions-should-not-hinder-oil-trade-with-india-2025-02-11/</link><description>俄罗斯第一任能源部长帕维尔·索罗金（Pavel Sorokin）周二表示，美国对俄罗斯的制裁不应影响莫斯科与印度的石油贸易，并补充说，评估最新限制的影响还为时过早。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 07:14:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-energy-official-says-us-sanctions-should-not-hinder-oil-trade-with-india-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>高级政府顾问说，印度不会很快取消对中国投资的禁令。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-expected-lift-ban-chinese-investments-soon-top-government-adviser-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>根据印度首席经济顾问V. Anantha Nageswaran周二的讲话，预计印度不会很快取消对中国投资的禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 06:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-not-expected-lift-ban-chinese-investments-soon-top-government-adviser-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>戈德曼说</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedgeflow-china-tops-hedge-funds-shopping-lists-so-far-this-year-goldman-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>高盛（Goldman Sachs）在一份报告中说，全球对冲基金在今年的大部分时间里一直在抢购中国股票，因为过去一周的购买加速了，因为本土人工智能创业公司的出现促进了投资者的热情。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 05:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedgeflow-china-tops-hedge-funds-shopping-lists-so-far-this-year-goldman-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>随着特朗普的新税率增加出口不确定性，中国钢铁制造商的股票滑行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shares-chinese-steelmakers-slide-trumps-fresh-tariffs-add-uncertainty-exports-2025-02-11/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的新征收对今年的钢铁出口产生影响的担忧，最高生产商中国主要的钢铁制造商的股票周二滑行。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 05:06:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/shares-chinese-steelmakers-slide-trumps-fresh-tariffs-add-uncertainty-exports-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>中国范克从州股东那里获得383亿美元的贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-gets-383-mln-loan-state-shareholder-2025-02-11/</link><description>现金短缺的中国范克说，其主要股东，国有深圳地铁（深圳地铁）正在向其提供28亿元人民币（3.8312亿美元）的贷款，在一个迹象中，政府正在加紧努力稳定房地产开发商。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 04:23:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-vanke-gets-383-mln-loan-state-shareholder-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-catl-plans-file-hong-kong-listing-application-raise-least-5-billion-this-2025-02-11/</link><description>根据对此事的直接了解，中国电池巨头CATL计划本周提交一份香港上市申请，以筹集至少50亿美元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 03:10:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-catl-plans-file-hong-kong-listing-application-raise-least-5-billion-this-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>官员说，香港将向WTO提出投诉。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-will-file-complaint-wto-us-tariffs-official-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>香港声称，美国无视该市作为单独的海关领土的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 02:40:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-will-file-complaint-wto-us-tariffs-official-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>XPeng，Geely分享在Byd提供免费的智能驾驶功能之后。</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-geely-autos-shares-fall-concerns-about-byds-smart-driving-push-2025-02-11/</link><description>中国汽车制造商Xpeng和Geely Auto的股票周二因担忧而跌倒，他们将努力与Byd的举动竞争，几乎在其所有车型上提供免费的智能驾驶功能。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 02:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-geely-autos-shares-fall-concerns-about-byds-smart-driving-push-2025-02-11/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉的上海巨型电池厂推出了生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/teslas-shanghai-megapack-battery-plant-launches-production-xinhua-says-2025-02-11/</link><description>中国官方新闻社新华社说，特斯拉在上海的电池巨型巨头制造了其巨型电池，已于周二推出了生产。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 01:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/teslas-shanghai-megapack-battery-plant-launches-production-xinhua-says-2025-02-11/</guid></item></channel></rss>